<br>
Teger the Tiny &lt;Gnome&gt; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.docsmooth.com/images/dot.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/31/02 1:05:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19147.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.totalnetsolutions.net/nightwatch/images/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Graffe.com Official Class Title Poll</span><hr size=1> all these people asking for &quot;Sorceror&quot; or &quot;Sorceress&quot; - how many people have pointed out that'd make you:<br>
